mil.nga.giat.geowave.analytic.mapreduce

Class GeoWaveAnalyticJobRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configured
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.analytic.mapreduce.GeoWaveAnalyticJobRunner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndependentJobRunner, MapReduceJobRunner, org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configurable, org.apache.hadoop.util.Tool
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConvexHullJobRunner, GroupAssigmentJobRunner, KMeansDistortionJobRunner, KMeansJobRunner, KSamplerJobRunner, NNJobRunner, UpdateCentroidCostJobRunner

    public abstract class GeoWaveAnalyticJobRunner
extends org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configured
implements org.apache.hadoop.util.Tool, MapReduceJobRunner, IndependentJobRunner
    This class managers the input and output formats for a map reduce job. It also controls job submission, isolating some of the job management responsibilities. One key benefit is support of unit testing for job runner instances.
